{
  "stem": "19690.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 65.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you always watched your back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Always.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't think I ever really got attacked.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I think the fear of the possibility, and the rocks and the words, were just as difficult for a six or seven-year-old as if they would have actually grabbed me and hit me.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jew, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Christ killer, and all these things that are normally said.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Jew, go away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jew, get out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Jew-- Jew boy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And these kind of things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a lot of these kids I knew by name because they were neighborhood kids.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they were not friends anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And where previously I could play on the street, it became very soon a factor that I could not leave our yard unless somebody was with me because they were always afraid of what could happen.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's why the weekends with my father, walking into the woods and walking along the Rhine, were such big treats.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One thing that sticks in my mind very vividly is we had a neighbor directly across the street from our living room.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when there was a specific headline in which was a Nazi newspaper, she would open her window, and sit in the window with the newspaper open so we could see.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she would sit there for hours, holding this newspaper to make sure that we saw what was in This would be maybe once a week, once a month.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whenever it was, whenever a big event happened, that was what would happen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We would see in We could also read-- listen to it on the radio.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she would make sure that we were aware of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The other thing we knew is that she was always watching our comings and goings.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
